22c3faa6d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNp=
U ]:=C2=A0
If your goal is to become one of the major players, you have to take riskie=
r bets, you have to put in more money. You have to do things that are less =
likely to pan out. But if it does pan out it=E2=80=99s going to be very imp=
actful.
One of those risky bets is making acquisitions so early in its life.=C2=A0
Over the past two and a half years, it=E2=80=99s put up its own capital to =
