7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].
These haven=E2=80=99t been the acquihires or yard sales, but good ol=E2=80=
=99 fashioned 1+1=3D3 M&A transactions. They=E2=80=99re a part of a specifi=
c strategy, based on those six bets.=C2=A0
I wanted to dig into Anduril=E2=80=99s M&A activity specifically because it=
