Every successful company has a =E2=80=9Cthing.=E2=80=9D Of all of the many =
things they do, there=E2=80=99s one that=E2=80=99s the secret sauce, the th=
ing they do better than anyone else. SpaceX can get kilograms to orbit more=
 cheaply than anyone else. Meta connects people. Google dominates search. B=
yteDance does addictive algorithmic feeds. Amazon is a logistics powerhouse=
=2E Microsoft sells software to enterprises.=C2=A0
Anduril=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Cthing=E2=80=9D isn=E2=80=99t any of its particul=
ar products, or even its Lattice OS; its thing is its ability to sell moder=
