That requires two broad capabilities:=C2=A0
Building Trust with the DoD
Having the Right Product at the Right Time
While Anduril is relatively young, it=E2=80=99s worth noting that its leade=
rs have run this playbook before. CEO Brian Schimpf, Executive Chairman Tra=
e Stephens, and COO Matt Grimm were all early employees at Palantir [ https=
://substack.com/redirect/20d0b738-0be2-46bc-b130-a20c6dfa8190?j=3DeyJ1IjoiO=
XAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], which built the =
