cess, so for Anduril, acquisitions speed the route to market.=C2=A0
As Steckman explained, =E2=80=9CBecause returns are so punctuated, and crea=
ting hardware takes many years to get right and to become trusted within a =
field, it is a way to accelerate your positioning against those big punctua=
ted movements.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
To date, the company has made five acquisitions across a range of capabilit=
ies:
