h analysis and data and they agree,=E2=80=9D he explained, =E2=80=9Csometim=
es the customer will acquire the exact thing you have.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
Second, being early lets you shape the narrative, not in a fluffy way, but =
=E2=80=9Cwith a lot of math and physics.=E2=80=9D It lets you go to the cus=
tomer and say =E2=80=9CWe=E2=80=99ve thought about this, done mathematical =
modeling and simulation, and here=E2=80=99s what we believe. But we also kn=
ow we could be wrong. Let=E2=80=99s talk about your problem and modify the =
