=A0
Anduril hasn=E2=80=99t been shy in sharing its narrative, backed by experie=
nce and expertise. Brose=E2=80=99s writing =E2=80=93 both his essays and hi=
s book, The Kill Chain [ https://substack.com/redirect/fe0de7a0-d04c-4e7b-a=
df6-044dfb12cd8d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m=
8ExkRNpU ], describe a future of warfare that they believe would be good fo=
