Porter-Price admitted that he=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Cspoiled in this job=E2=80=
=9D:=C2=A0
No one on the team asks me about a discount rate or whether we=E2=80=99re p=
aying 15x EBITDA. We=E2=80=99re not trying to find cost synergies. All of t=
