or: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0=
;"><strong>Bet #1: The way humans fight wars, or more importantly deter eac=
h other from fighting wars in the first place, is changing</strong><span>: =
from large, expensive, exquisite hardware platforms to distributed systems =
of smaller, cheaper, more networked defense products.</span></p><p style=3D=
"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
