64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">I wanted to d=
ig into Anduril&#8217;s M&amp;A activity specifically because it stands out=
 as a unique company-building strategy for such a young startup. After conv=
ersations with the team and dozens of hours of research, Anduril&#8217;s ac=
quisitions have illuminated what makes Anduril tick, and why I think it has=
 a real shot at becoming a sixth Defense Prime alongside Lockheed Martin, B=
oeing, Raytheon, Northrop Grumman, and General Dynamics.&#160;&#160;</p><p =
style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 20px 0;">Every successful company has a &#8220;thing.&#8221; Of all o=
