erhouse. Microsoft sells software to enterprises.&#160;</p><p style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;=
"><span>Anduril&#8217;s &#8220;thing&#8221; isn&#8217;t any of its particul=
ar products, or even its Lattice OS; </span><strong>its thing is its abilit=
