ont-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-lef=
t: 4px;"><strong>Wins Can Be Massive.</strong><span> These programs can be =
absolutely enormous. The Joint Strike Fighter program, awarded to Lockheed =
Martin in 2001 to produce 2,456 F-35 Lightning II fighter jets through 2044=
, is currently estimated to cost </span><strong>$1.7 trillion</strong><span=
>. Lockheed still owns the contract despite the fact that its costs have ba=
