ernment pays the contractor&#8217;s cost with a margin on top, Lockheed mak=
es </span><em>more </em><span>money the more over budget it is.&#160;</span=
></p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">While JSF is the largest, it&#8217;s certa=
