</a><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Dive fit the future model of war that Anduril is buil=
ding against: smaller, cheaper, autonomous systems across all domains (land=
, air, sea, and space) coordinated through software. But part of the balanc=
e is figuring out which parts of that future will occur when.&#160;</p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Steckman told me that Anduril asks two questions for al=
l organic product development and acquisitions: </span><strong>&#8220;Is th=
e problem urgent and can we solve it in less than 5 years?&#8221;&#160;</st=
rong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Dive fit the bill on both fronts:&#160;</p><ul s=
tyle=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-=
