 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; =
padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Urgent:</strong><span> Submarines are critical =
in the conflict with China, and we&#8217;re retiring exquisite nuclear subm=
arines faster than we can build them. We need cheaper, faster-to-build subm=
arines for their stealth, deterrence, intelligence gathering, and more, now=
=2E&#160;</span></p></li><li style=3D"ma=
