d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">sold into a</a=
><span> &#8220;$100 million co-funded design, development and manufacturing=
 program for Extra Large Autonomous Undersea Vehicles (XL-AUVs) for the Roy=
al Australian Navy.&#8221; By December, Anduril execs flew to Australia for=
 the naming ceremony for the AUV. They call it </span><strong>Ghost Shark</=
strong><span>.&#160;</span></p><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/be2=
4fd9b-c0b2-4cf2-a1fd-f2885dbfbc38?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZ=
jmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"youtube-wrap" data-co=
mponent-name=3D"Youtube2ToDOMStatic" style=3D"display: block; margin: 1.6em=
 0;"><img src=3D"https://substackcdn.com/image/youtube/w_550,c_limit/l_yout=
