also serve as a test run the US Navy uses to evaluate purchasing Dive-LD AU=
Vs for its own fleet.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">With Dive, Anduril is skat=
ing where the puck is clearly heading and delivering capabilities, and reve=
nue, now.&#160;</p><h4 class=3D"header-with-anchor-widget" style=3D"-moz-ap=
