 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"><strong>Adranos Energetics</strong></h4>=
<p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; mar=
gin: 0 0 20px 0;">&#8220;Our process takes a year,&#8221; Porter-Price told=
 me when I asked about the lifecycle of an acquisition at Anduril.&#160;</p=
><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;">Each year, Anduril&#8217;s leadership team comes up with=
 a shopping list, identifying areas that fit within programs they want to p=
ursue.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>One such area on the shopping list =
was solid rocket motors (SRMs). After Northrop Grumman acquired Orbital ATK=
, the maker of the nation&#8217;s largest rocket motor, Boeing abandoned th=
e ICBM business it&#8217;d been in with the Minuteman for half a century, c=
iting the fact that the acquisition gave Northrop &#8220;an unfair advantag=
e.&#8221; The </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/21a90b4d-e129=
-44f5-86b5-0dd335d1af51?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbq=
Osa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: unde=
rline;">Pentagon warned Congress</a><span> of the dangers of SRM consolidat=
ion in 2017, and the FY </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/1e7=
d37be-996e-4324-b95f-915811e83dec?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZ=
jmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decora=
tion: underline;">2024 DoD Budget</a><span>, submitted in March 2023, notes=
 that the Future Year Defense Plan (FYDP), essentially a five-year defense =
roadmap, &#8220;applies resources to address supply chain bottlenecks in &#=
8230; Solid Rocket manufacturing,&#8221; among others.</span></p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">It didn&#8217;t take much of a crystal ball to understand that th=
e DoD would be willing to spend on solid rocket motors, and looking at how =
Anduril attacked that opportunity gives us a glimpse into its process.</p><=
p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; marg=
in: 0 0 20px 0;">So SRMs were on the list, and Porter-Price and his team we=
nt shopping.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; =
line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">He says they identified about ten S=
RM companies in the US and Australia. Then they met with each of them, did =
technical diligence, and &#8220;spent a lot of time on planes&#8221; gettin=
g to know everyone in the ecosystem. They honed in on three companies that =
were particularly good.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">None of these companies =
is for sale. No banker is shopping them. But none of them is stupid, either=
=2E &#8220;They know what it means when=
 the head of corp dev comes to visit,&=
#8221; he admitted. One of the three companies Anduril was interested in wa=
s Adranos Energetics, which manufactures its SRMs in Mississippi.&#160;</p>=
<p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; mar=
gin: 0 0 20px 0;">&#8220;I went to Mississippi seven or eight times with pe=
ople on our team, we brought them out to California. Everyone wants to know=
 what Palmer&#8217;s like,&#8221; Porter-Price said, &#8220;It&#8217;s unco=
mfortably like dating.&#8221;&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">It&#8217;s importa=
nt that both sides get to know each other. Many of these companies are boot=
strapped. They&#8217;re the founders&#8217; babies. And joining forces with=
 Anduril means they&#8217;ll no longer be their own boss. In return, Anduri=
l structures deals to incentivize founders with significant ownership in th=
e combined company, which they need to earn by coming to work and often run=
ning divisions. This is a long-term relationship.&#160;</p><p style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;=
">At a certain point, they have a discussion on a couple different paths th=
ey can follow:&#160;</p><ol style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=
=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(6=
4, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0=
; padding-left: 4px;">Partner or Collaborate</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8=
px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); f=
ont-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-lef=
t: 4px;">Become One Company</p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">In Adranos&#8217=
; case, they decided to become one company.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb=
(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">At t=
hat point in the process, Porter-Price explained, Anduril &#8220;puts toget=
her a compelling package for the founding team&#8221; and wants them to bri=
ng their whole team with them, and then they go fast. Typically, they go fr=
om LOI to execution in 60 days, although it can take longer in some cases, =
like it did with Adranos, because greater diligence was required because ag=
encies like the ATF expect you to be careful with rocket motors.&#160;</p><=
p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; marg=
in: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>In June, </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redi=
